"na pāhuneyyo na dakkhiṇeyyo na añjalikaraṇīyo na anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ "
"lokassa."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant with five qualities is not worthy of offerings "
"dedicated to the gods, not worthy of hospitality, not worthy of a teacher’s "
"offering, not worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is not a supreme "
"field of merit for the world."

msgctxt "an5.139:8.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.139:8.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkhamo hoti rūpānaṃ, akkhamo saddānaṃ, akkhamo "
"gandhānaṃ, akkhamo rasānaṃ, akkhamo phoṭṭhabbānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant can’t endure sights, sounds, smells, tastes, and "
"touches."

