msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, hearing a sound with their ears, is not aroused by "
"desirable sounds, so is able to still the mind."

msgctxt "an5.139:24.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti saddānaṃ. (2)"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant can endure sounds."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "an5.139:25.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti gandhānaṃ."
msgstr "And how is it that a mendicant can endure smells?"

msgctxt "an5.139:25.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ghānena gandhaṃ ghāyitvā rajanīye gandhe na "
"sārajjati, sakkoti cittaṃ samādahituṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, smelling an odor with their nose, is not aroused by a "
"desirable smell, so is able to still the mind."

msgctxt "an5.139:25.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti gandhānaṃ. (3)"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant can endure smells."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "an5.139:26.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti rasānaṃ?"
msgstr "And how is it that a mendicant can endure tastes?"

msgctxt "an5.139:26.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu jivhāya rasaṃ sāyitvā rajanīye rase na sārajjati, "
"sakkoti cittaṃ samādahituṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, tasting a flavor with their tongue, is not aroused by "
"desirable tastes, so is able to still the mind."

msgctxt "an5.139:26.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti rasānaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant can endure tastes."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "an5.139:27.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti phoṭṭhabbānaṃ?"
msgstr "And how is it that a mendicant can endure touches?"

msgctxt "an5.139:27.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāyena phoṭṭhabbaṃ phusitvā rajanīye phoṭṭhabbe na "
"sārajjati, sakkoti cittaṃ samādahituṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant, feeling a touch with their body, is not aroused by a "
"desirable touch, so is able to still the mind."

msgctxt "an5.139:27.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu khamo hoti phoṭṭhabbānaṃ. (5)"
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant can endure touches."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "an5.139:28.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti "
"pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these five qualities is worthy of offerings dedicated to "
"the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, worthy of "
"veneration with joined palms, and is a supreme field of merit for the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.139:28.2"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
